      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a beautiful luster, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is sound, having received regular servicing, and it drives smoothly with no known issues. It represents a great value for someone looking for a reliable, attractive vehicle that has been treated with care.",
