      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been garage-kept and pampered since day one\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in truly flawless shape, inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
