    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated zenith. The S54 power plant features a fully documented dual-VANOS overhaul and upgraded rod bearings, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with mechanical harmony. Power is transmitted via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential. Crucially, the rear subframe mounting points have been structurally reinforced, preserving the chassis's legendary 50/50 weight distribution and torsional rigidity. The exterior retains original paint depth, while the interior shows no bolster fatigue or LCD pixel degradation. This is a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and historical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. All service records included. Flawless interior and exterior.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
