    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, museum-quality 2004 BMW M3, finished in the iconic and rare Laguna Seca Blue over a flawless Black Nappa leather interior. This vehicle has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment its entire life, showing absolutely no signs of wear, stone chips, or interior aging. The paint maintains a deep, glass-like luster, and the factory wheels are free of any blemishes. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from new, with a complete, documented service history from day one. Every switch, dial, and pixel functions perfectly, and the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of. This is a rare opportunity for a serious collector to acquire a showroom-fresh example of the legendary E46 platform. No modifications, no stories, just pure automotive perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
